  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms </strong>sleep up to two people and have a TV, tea &amp; coffee making facilities, safe, minibar, hairdryer and a bath or shower. Single rooms are also available.</p>
<p><strong>Comfort Rooms </strong>can sleep up to three people and have a lounge/seating area.</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe </strong>sleep two and have a shower and bath. They are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Junior Suite </strong>sleep up to four people and offer more space with a seating area. They are available on request, please call to book.</p>
<p>Balconies can be requested across the room types but are never guaranteed.  </p>]]></roomsDescription>
